<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
This species was placed in the 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Arborescens</emphasis>
group by McPherson (1981) but both nuclear data and 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">ITS</emphasis>
indicate its more correctly placed in the 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Jalapa</emphasis>
radiation, to which it conforms morphologically.
</paragraph>
